# Immediate Borrower Liability Amount

## identifier
de8747

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for immediate borrower liability representing all on-balance sheet financial liabilities, excluding derivative contracts and borrowing of securities, gold and other precious metals without cash collateral.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.ClaimsCrossBorder.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
